d valign=top background=http://www.cafenet.plus.com/The_Magicians_Tower/Images/Background_1.gif class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/upixelssoulscreamsh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pixels Soulscream SH</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(4/5/02 3:13:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Stormhammer Guild Looking for skilled Summoners</span><hr size=1> Hello, <br>
Science of War is a guild in formation on the Stormhammer server and is now recruiting highly-qualified players. <br>
<br>
If you are interested in applying, we ask you to visit our website at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.scienceofwar.net">www.scienceofwar.net</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> and get to know us. Read the FAQs, evaluate our goals, familiarize yourself with our recruiting requirements, and spend a little time thinking about whether you'd also like to apply for a position of officership (we primarily need class recruiters and class leaders right now (we don't have a Mage class leader yet!). <br>
<br>
Thanks, and good luck.<br>
<br>
We know that there is a core of extremely talented players on the Stormhammer server, and we aim to get them into this guild so that we can do things that are not done on other Everquest servers. Isn't it time that the &quot;Legends&quot; environment lived up to its moniker? Let's create a great guild.<br>
<br>
<br>
PS: The flames vs. legends have all been aired by now and are getting pretty old. Can we please not go there? <br>
