 intentionally there. I have yet to have a rare spawn KS'd. I haven't once been begged for a PL, gear, cash, etc., by some level 60's twink. Just seems like a nicer neighborhood to me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uyanbun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yanbun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#333333>(4/6/02 3:42:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Stormhammer Guild Looking for skilled Summoners</span><hr size=1> I brought my twink Cleric. Its great, I'm one of the few low level clerics around. Groups need me. Its fun, just far too many high levels around to be healthy.<br>
